snippet.title: Super Mario Sunshine Seaside - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Sunshine Seaside is my mod of New Super Mario Bros. U for Wii U.
In this 1-world mod, Mario ventures off to a sunny tropical island, exploring 8 unique levels in his quest to defeat Bowser Jr.
The mod is now released, and you can find the download link here: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1JhNxihF6BxheJrvtb3YAnOHfYY9MZ78Y?usp=sharing
The trailer was recorded and edited by ​⁠@Rimea.

This trailer was also shown in the New Super Mario Bros. Franchise Modding Direct (2023) by Rimea: https://youtu.be/40OUE8quoz4

Sunshine Seaside's Gamebanana Page: https://gamebanana.com/wips/67330
